gameDetails.description:
Imperial Settlers: Aztecs, unlike previous expansions to Imperial Settlers, comes without common cards.

The 10 common cards for the Imperial Settlers: Aztecs (10C001 - 10C010) are made available as a separate expansion for the game.

First release was provided in 2016 to early buyers of Imperial Settlers: Aztecs, who received a copy with incorrect EGY070 card (Egyptian card with Japanese back).
